[These figures indicate that the various strategies designed to contain and reverse the measles outbreaks that afflict the UK are beginning to take effect and that the magnitude of the outbreaks will decline significantly in subsequent months. Of special interest are the data showing that most of the cases with an onset date in July 2013 are D8 genotype. The MVs/Taunton.GBR/27.12/ [D8] strain continues to be the main virus type, but with a cluster of cases of a different D8 strain in the South West region, and sporadic genotype B3 strains in a couple of regions. - Mod.CP

